/**
* Basic Hotstrings
* Auto-replace text as you type
*/

; Type "btw" followed by space/tab/enter, it becomes "by the way"
::btw::by the way

; Common abbreviations
::omw::on my way
::brb::be right back
::ty::thank you
::yw::you're welcome

; Email address shortcut
::@@::yourname@email.com

; Longer text expansions
::addr::
(
123 Main Street
City, State 12345
Phone: (555) 123-4567
)

; Unicode symbols
::shrug::¯\_(ツ)_/¯
